OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784575122
OL,3,CGloucestershire police chief accused
OL,4,Cof misconduct to leave job
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of Gloucestershire
OL,7,FPolice, who is accused of gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct, is set to leave his
OL,9,Fposition.
OL,11,FThe force said Rod Hansen's contract
OL,12,Fexpires at the end of July and he will
OL,13,Fbe leaving his role as the police and
OL,14,Fcrime commissioner.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
