PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784575122
OL,3,CGloucestershire police chief accused
OL,4,Cof misconduct to leave job
OL,6,FHe was suspended from the role in
OL,7,FOctober 2024 after the Independent
OL,8,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC)
OL,9,Fconcluded he should face a gross
OL,10,Fmisconduct hearing over allegations he
OL,11,Ffailed to appropriately act on a
OL,12,Freport of a data breach.
OL,14,FHe denies any wrongdoing.
OL,16,FHansen was due to attend a misconduct
OL,17,Fpanel this week but the hearing was
OL,18,Fpostponed, citing legal reasons.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784575122
OL,3,CGloucestershire police chief accused
OL,4,Cof misconduct to leave job
OL,6,FThe panel will instead be resumed in
OL,7,FDecember, even though he will no
OL,8,Flonger be working with Gloucestershire
OL,9,FPolice.
OL,11,FThe IOPC said the allegations
OL,12,Fconcerned whether Mr Hansen did not
OL,13,Fsufficiently act on information passed
OL,14,Fto him in October 2022.
OL,16,FAccording to the IOPC, this related to
OL,17,Fa staff member suspected of carrying
OL,18,Fout an unauthorised search of police
OL,19,Fsystems - and accessing third party
OL,20,Fpersonal data ` linked to a road
OL,21,Ftraffic collision.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
