OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784575122
OL,3,CGloucestershire police chief accused
OL,4,Cof misconduct to leave job
OL,6,FThe collision took place in September
OL,7,F2022, but concerns over Mr Hansen's
OL,8,Fresponse to the matter only came to
OL,9,Flight in 2024.
OL,11,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Chris
OL,12,FNelson made a referral to the police
OL,13,Fwatchdog in August 2024 and a gross
OL,14,Fmisconduct notice was issued.
OL,16,FMr Hansen was suspended and Maggie
OL,17,FBlyth was appointed interim chief
OL,18,Fconstable. She is now temporary chief
OL,19,Fconstable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
