OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784575122
OL,3,CGloucestershire police chief accused
OL,4,Cof misconduct to leave job
OL,6,FAn IOPC spokesman said an
OL,7,Finvestigation concluded Mr Hansen has
OL,8,Fa case to answer for gross misconduct
OL,9,Frelating to challenging and reporting
OL,10,Fimproper conduct; discreditable
OL,11,Fconduct; duties and responsibilities;
OL,12,Fhonesty and integrity; and orders and
OL,13,Finstructions.
OL,15,FHe was served a second gross
OL,16,Fmisconduct notice in May 2025 after
OL,17,Fbeing accused of being improperly
OL,18,Finvolved in the recruitment of a
OL,19,Fmember of staff. This was later
OL,20,Fdropped after an IOPC investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
