PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784575122
OL,3,CGloucestershire police chief accused
OL,4,Cof misconduct to leave job
OL,6,FHansen became the Chief Constable of
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police in 2017. He has
OL,8,Fa Queen's Police Medal and used to
OL,9,Fserve at Avon and Somerset Police.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
